description: SqlPackage is a command-line utility that automates database development tasks by exposing some of the public Data-Tier Application Framework (DacFx) APIs.
releaseNotes: New public APIs to deploy with parquet format. Fixes a bug when use of functions in APPLY clause of view can result deploy failure. Fixes a bug when a script has clustered index on a variable
